data.description: Come see this beautiful home built in 2022 still under remainder of builder's 2-10 home warranty! This home is loaded with upgrades. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances with the stove and refrigerator being under warranty until 2026, a tile backsplash, granite countertops, soft close white cabinets, an 8 foot serving bar, and a dinette area with sliding glass doors. The spacious master bedroom includes a large walk in closet and has a private door leading to the 24'x12' enclosed lanai. The ensuite master bath features a 7 ft dual vanity with granite countertop, and a tiled walk in shower with a custom glass door. Split bedroom plan offering privacy to guests or family, with its own bathroom that also has a granite countertop vanity. Inside laundry room for ultimate convenience. The 2 car garage has an epoxy floor. Whole house gutters, privacy fenced backyard, and an additional concrete pad perfect for grilling right outside the lanai. Don't wait to build, come snag this better than new, move in ready home today!
